data.title: Famous birthdays list for today, April 26, 2024 includes celebrities Jet Li, Jordana Brewster
data.meta_description: Jet Li and Jordana Brewster share a birthday today. Check out our photo slideshow of celebrities and other famous people with birthdays on April 26, 2024 and find out a fun fact about each person.
data.text:

Fun fact: Was born in Beijing, China

Actor Kevin James turns 59

Fun fact: Has appeared as a panelist on ‘Hollywood Squares’
